						<summary>

						<p>Hoysaḷa, Vīra-Sōmēśvara, 5th = A.D. 1240.</p>						

						<p>In the beginning there is a short Sanskrit <hi rend="italic">praśasti</hi> of the king. The record gives the arbitration of the king in favour of the temple on a land dispute between the temple trustees and an individual regarding the ownership of the village Vaṇṇam <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Madurāntakanallūr.</p>						

